    "Other nonconvex constraints are readily handled by heuristics that involve solving just a handful of convex problems.",
    "One general method is called relax-round-solve [DTB18].",
    "We illustrate this method to handle the constraint that the minimum nonzero weight absolute value is 0.001 (10 bps).",
